{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/About_the_game.jpg?t=1736421424\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the hauntingly immersive world of <strong>The Saint </strong>, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">a first-person <strong>psychological horror</strong> game set in the eerie realm of Liminal spaces, with a VHS look.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into a surreal dreamscape where fog shrouds your every move and the line between reality and nightmare blurs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your mission: unravel the cryptic puzzles that block your escape and find your way out of this unsettling dream. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Drawing inspiration from the chilling atmosphere of <strong>Silent Hill</strong>, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Saint </strong>,  will test your nerves and your wits in an unforgettable journey through the depths of fear. Are you ready to confront the darkness and escape the dream?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/Walk_Dream_GIF.gif?t=1736421424\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/Features___Mechanics.jpg?t=1736421424\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immersive Horror experience: An atmospheric, Foggy environment, inspired by <strong>Silent Hill 2</strong>, with a believable environment, intensifies the horror experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Psychological horror experience: The game will make you question everything and drive you insane. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the eerie beauty of liminal spaces\u2014where you're alone, but never truly alone.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unravel intricate puzzles and uncover hidden mysteries\u2014each step brings a new challenge and a deeper secret.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unsettled environment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in psychological horror\u2014no jump scares, just pure, mind-bending terror.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/Walk_Red_Door_GIF.gif?t=1736421424\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/BigMonster_Walk_GIF.gif?t=1736421424\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/addtowishlist_gif.gif?t=1736421424\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736421424","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/page.bg.jpg?t=1736421424","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/baa6e43b60ff196ac0d8f6dffae588f98305f952/capsule_231x87_alt_assets_0.jpg?t=1736421424","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/baa6e43b60ff196ac0d8f6dffae588f98305f952/capsule_184x69_alt_assets_0.jpg?t=1736421424","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"This Game may contain content not appropriate for all ages, or may not be suitable for viewing at work: Frequent Violence or Gore."},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h1>THE SAINT</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/THE_SAINT_LOGO.png?t=1736421424\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></p><br><h1>BACK STORY</h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/backstory.jpg?t=1736421424\" /><br><br>After a long shift, Alex left the office well past midnight. Construction blocked his usual route home, forcing him to take the infamous forest road. Dark tales surrounded this path\u2014whispers of eerie disappearances and haunted souls. Yet, it was his only option.<br><br>The storm began as he entered the forest. Rain lashed against the windshield, and the dense canopy overhead turned the road into a tunnel of shadows. His headlights struggled to pierce the gloom, and the wind howled through the trees, making them groan ominously.<br><br>Shadows flitted at the edges of his vision, and every twist and turn looked the same. Anxiety gnawed at him. Was he still on the right path, or hopelessly lost? Lightning flashed, revealing the way forward for a heartbeat before plunging it back into darkness.<br><br>Suddenly, a faint light appeared ahead. Hope surged within him. He accelerated, desperate to reach it. But as he rounded the final bend, the forest seemed to close tighter, the darkness thickening.<br><br>Would he find his way home, or join the lost souls of the forest? The answer remained hidden in the shadows.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/Car_Cut_GIF.gif?t=1736421424\" /></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/About_the_game.jpg?t=1736421424\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the 